      <div class="card">
        <h2>⚡ Olympian Gods — the 12 beings behind the zodiac</h2>
        <p>The peer pantheon to the Hindu devas and Norse gods. The Greek Olympians every zodiac sign on gab44 has been invoking silently — Aries is Ares, Libra is Aphrodite, Sagittarius is Zeus, Pisces is Poseidon. Three families. <strong>Cronid sovereigns</strong> (gold / rose / sea-blue / wheat): <em>Zeus</em> the thunderer-king, <em>Hera</em> the queen of heaven, <em>Poseidon</em> the earth-shaker, <em>Demeter</em> the grain-mother of the Eleusinian Mysteries. <strong>Bright Olympians</strong> (grey-eyed / sun-gold / moon-silver / rose): <em>Athena</em> wisdom-strategist, <em>Apollo</em> prophecy-music-healing-plague, <em>Artemis</em> lady of wild things, <em>Aphrodite</em> foam-born desire. <strong>Workshop & ecstatic</strong> (crimson / forge-bronze / mercury / wine-purple): <em>Ares</em> slayer of men, <em>Hephaestus</em> the lame smith, <em>Hermes</em> the messenger-psychopomp, <em>Dionysus</em> the twice-born dying-and-rising god. Each page: Homer-Hesiod source-honest (Iliad, Theogony, the Homeric Hymns, Euripides Bacchae, Apollodorus, Pausanias), iconography, invocation (Tuesday-Mars, Wednesday-Mercury, Thursday-Jupiter, Friday-Venus across Romance languages), in love + in work, the gift, the shadow (19th-c. Hellenist-supremacist appropriation, sanitized rape-myths in Zeus & Apollo, white-marble fantasy, Nazi-era Olympia, Disney/Percy Jackson flattening — named honestly per god), paired zodiac sign + planet.</p>
